   and mitigation strategies, such as cybersecurity training programs, organizational policies, and technological solutions, is needed to address the identified antecedents and minimize the consequences of data
   breaches.
   In conclusion, this literature review provides a comprehensive synthesis of existing research on the
   antecedents and consequences of data breaches. By integrating findings from various disciplines and
   methodologies, it highlights the multifaceted nature of data breaches and emphasizes the need for interdisciplinary approaches to address this complex issue. The identified knowledge gaps and future research
   directions provide valuable insights for researchers and practitioners aiming to enhance cybersecurity
   practices and mitigate the negative consequences of data breaches.
